    <fr:title text="Forester 3.1 › removal of undocumented \LaTeX output"><fr:link href="foreign-forester-jms-00HY.xml" title="Forester 3.1" addr="forest://forester/jms-00HY" type="local">Forester 3.1</fr:link> › removal of undocumented <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\LaTeX ]]></fr:tex> output</fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Change</fr:taxon>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>Previously, Forester would emit <html:code>.tex</html:code> files for each of your trees in the <html:code>latex</html:code> directory. This feature has been removed, as <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\LaTeX ]]></fr:tex> can be generated more reliably using XSLT. Please see the <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/forester-to-latex" type="external">forester-to-latex</fr:link> repository for an example stylesheet.</html:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
